-- Iraq Wants Kurdish Authorities to Hand Over Proceeds of Oil Sales to Iran
-- Kadhim Ajrash
-- 2010-07-25T13:57:58Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-25/iraq-wants-kurdish-authorities-to-hand-over-proceeds-of-oil-sales-to-iran.html

          
          
             The Iraqi government wants the
Kurdish provincial authorities to stop exporting oil products to
Iran and to hand over the proceeds of these sales to the
Treasury in Baghdad, Iraqi Oil Minister Hussain Al-Shahristani
told reporters today in Baghdad.  
